    "htmlContent": "<h2>Core Playbook</h2>\n<p>Juno uses Glide Boost and Hyper Ring to stay mobile with her team&#39;s dive, healing on the move with Pulsar Torpedoes and clearing crowd control with Orbital Ray during a fight.</p>\n<h2>Tactical Caveats</h2>\n<p>Her healing is spread thin across a wide moving group rather than concentrated, so a single ally under focused burst fire can still die despite her being nearby.</p>\n"
